ru.dest.library.object

Class CommandRegistry<T extends org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin>

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.dest.library.object.CommandRegistry<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - - your main class

    public final class CommandRegistry<T extends org.bukkit.plugin.java.JavaPlugin>
extends Object
    This Class is designed to register various types of commands.
    An object of this class has already been created for each BukkitPlugin, you can get it via BukkitPlugin.commandRegistry();
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    DestKoder
